tor.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=ext.smw.style%7Cext.smw.tooltip.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<script async=\"\" src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=startup&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector\"></script>\n<meta name=\"ResourceLoaderDynamicStyles\" content=\"\"/>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=site.styles&amp;only=styles&amp;skin=vector\"/>\n<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"MediaWiki 1.30.0\"/>\n<link rel=\"ExportRDF\" type=\"application/rdf+xml\" title=\"Ring of Shadows\" href=\"/index.php?title=Special:ExportRDF/Ring_of_Shadows&amp;xmlmime=rdf\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"CrawlWiki (en)\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/resources/lib/html5shiv/html5shiv.min.js?40bd4\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Ring_of_Shadows rootpage-Ring_of_Shadows skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Ring of Shadows</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f90; background-color: #fc6; border-left: 15px solid #f90; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.30\" title=\"0.30\">0.30</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A black ring that can make its wearer one with the shadows. It surrounds you with an aura of shadow, increasing your stealth and reducing the accuracy of all others within it.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><a href=\"/File:Ring_of_shadows.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ring of shadows.png\" src=\"/images/e/ec/Ring_of_shadows.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <i><b>the ring of Shadows</b></i><br />\nGenerates a 3-tile <a href=\"/Umbra\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Umbra\">umbra</a><br />\nAllows the wearer to turn <a href=\"/Invisibility_(ego)\" title=\"Invisibility (ego)\">invisible</a><br />\n+50 <a href=\"/Stealth\" title=\"Stealth\">Stealth</a><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mechanics\">Mechanics</span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/Umbra\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Umbra\">umbra</a> increases the wearer's stealth score by +50%, applied after the ring's +50 bonus.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Also, any affected monster inside the umbra has its <a href=\"/Accuracy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Accuracy\">accuracy</a> reduced by avg. 3.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/Undead\" title=\"Undead\">Undead</a> and <a href=\"/Demonic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Demonic\">demonic</a> monsters are immune to the accuracy penalty, as well as <a href=\"/Death_knight\" title=\"Death knight\">death knights</a>.\n</p><p>If you are worshipping <a href=\"/Dithmenos\" title=\"Dithmenos\">Dithmenos</a>, only the higher of the two umbra stealth bonuses are used. So a 6* Dithmenos worshipper will get a total of x2 stealth from their god; a 1* worshiper will get x1.5 from the ring of Shadows.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Desirability\">Desirability</span></h2>\n<p>The <b>ring of Shadows</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> is a nice find for stealthy characters. The umbra boosts stealth, and even for 0 stealth brutes, it increases your chance to dodge attacks. However, a <a href=\"/Ring_of_evasion\" title=\"Ring of evasion\">ring of evasion</a> or <a href=\"/Ring_of_protection\" title=\"Ring of protection\">protection</a> will offer better defense once an enemy notices you.\n</p><p>Any character can keep this ring around as a swapout, in case you want to evoke invisibility. Due to the <a href=\"/Drain\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Drain\">drain</a> this ability causes (even if you fail), it is recommended to have good <a href=\"/Evocations\" title=\"Evocations\">Evocations</a> before evoking it.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.28\" title=\"0.28\">0.28</a>, the ring's umbra penalized the wearer's accuracy.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>, evoking invisibility did not <a href=\"/Drain\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Drain\">drain</a> the user.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.19\" title=\"0.19\">0.19</a>, it had <a href=\"/See_invisible\" title=\"See invisible\">see invisible</a> and rN+ instead of a +50 Stealth bonus.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.14\" title=\"0.14\">0.14</a>, it had +4 EV and -4 accuracy instead of umbra.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.1/crawl-ref/source/player.cc#L3135\">player.cc:3135</a> (0.30.1)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.1/crawl-ref/source/attack.h#L17\">attack.h:17</a> (0.30.1)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.1/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L1084\">art-data.txt:1084</a> (0.30.1)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916011925\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.008 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.084 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.400 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 111/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 356/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1667/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 292/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive par